node.text:
Team Shroom or Team Chick? Still a tough one, though Shroom is a winner for me with those melty cheese and portobello mushroom!

#circuitbreaker doesn’t stop us from having @shakeshacksg at home. Had satisfying lunch complete with Crinkle Cut Fries and Coffee Shake. Recommend for coffee addicts like me to get this Shake, since the joe is from Common Man Coffee.

Shake Shack
Address: 89 Neil Road, Singapore 088849
#shakeshacksg #shakeshack #savefnbsg #CassStayHome
@crappysotong yes but best eaten there cos it wasn’t quite as melty at home
@365days2play hahaha cos I can’t take beef, so no option
@kimmmywan just sth that will get you craving for it right
@cassakating definitely! Just can't get enough of the cheese + portobello! 🤤🤤
@kimmmywan 🤣 IKR!!! And pair with their crinkle cut fries the best
Team shroom here too! Those melty cheese 🤤
@mysweetlittletooth LOLS same! I can’t take beef either heheh.
I can only eat this 2 since I can’t eat beef and I’ll go for shrooms over chicken too! 👍🏻😋 Love the oozy cheese within🤩
@cforcassan hehehe sld be shorter queue now
So gonna get Shake Shack this weekend!!! 😍
@wafflenessa really? Time to go try try! I first had it in Dubai and tot was good~
